OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAll parts will have a dry day
OL,6,Fwith variable amounts of cloud and
OL,7,Fsome bright or sunny spells. Best of
OL,8,Fthe sunshine in the east.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FMainly dry this evening with
OL,11,Fjust the odd shower. Then outbreaks of
OL,12,Frain will spread northeast for a time
OL,13,Fovernight before it turns drier later.
OL,14,
OL,15,CTuesday:FVariable amounts of cloud and
OL,16,Fsunny spells along with scattered slow
OL,17,Fmoving showers, occasionally heavy in
OL,18,Fthe afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
